Trailers is an application that will pull trailers from some service 
(currently the trailers come from Apple's "current.xml").

********************************************************************************
Currently Implemented Features
********************************************************************************
-- Pull Trailers from a feed
-- Load Trailers into the store after adding a guid and parsing the XML
-- Display Trailers in a Listview using new MasterDetailView 
-- Show details of selected Trailer 
   -- ( Poster, Rating, ReleaseDate, Description, and Trailer )
-- Use SC.VideoView to allow the trailer to be played on Desktop and iPad.

